Annotation Type JsonPolymorphicTypeMap.TypeDef


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public static @interface JsonPolymorphicTypeMap.TypeDef
    Declares a mapping between a key value and a referenced class.

      Required Elements
